# matches(of:)

**Instance Method**

Returns a collection containing all matches of the specified regex.

## Declaration

```swift
func matches<Output>(of r: some RegexComponent) -> [Regex<Output>.Match]
```

## Return Value

A collection of matches of `regex`.
